---
title: Creamy Orkney Crab and King Prawn Linguine with Lemon, Chives and Rocket
description: Make a meal that's truly special with this lightly indulgent and luxurious Creamy Orkney Crab and King Prawn Linguine.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R32_W30_UK_SPR23307-4_Main_low-3c2c8632.jpg
